name: Hunters of the Soaring Dunes
description: Hailing from the Rootmason capital city of Thespin, the Hunters of the Soaring Dunes are known for their adept handling of dune surfers. Now equipped with detailed knowledge of all the birds across Kharth, and the ability to communicate with them, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
